{"tid":2061231,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"北京多兩人確診新型肺炎　為昨日確診個案同事","createTime":"2020-06-12T08:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T15:48:17.000Z","uid":5195,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9a4a540649b4caaf15184e7252799788dbd7da35","tid":2061231,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:42:04.000Z","msg":"北京市今日再新增兩宗新型肺炎確診個案，兩名患者來自豐台區，是昨日確診個案的同一單位員工。<br />\n<br />\n新個案的其中一人在潛伏期內曾到青島出差，另外一人則沒有外遊記錄，現時在定點醫療機構隔離治療。當局已加大社區管控力度，對患者所在小區及單位進行封閉式管理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531675-20200612.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531675-20200612.htm&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjBjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=c9ace58b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531675-20200612.htm&h=d2a89196\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531675-20200612.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"213f541bfa7a195e6ca66c99bde17f0e242417f8","tid":2061231,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:59:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06fac4e7747355b7ec090651d2f2aef7f15f33bb","tid":2061231,"uid":145273,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T09:00:11.000Z","msg":"大爆發again <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /